  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to gnome-packagekit</title>

    <para><application>gnome-packagekit</application> is the collection of graphical
    tools for <application>PackageKit</application> to be used in the
    <application>GNOME</application> desktop.</para>

    &lfs68_built;

